review:
@capcom you guys made it really hard for me to convince my friend evan to get into this game. I've had to resort to the lowest form of gaslighting, lying, deception, falsehood, dishonesty and corruption to hide the fact that this game doesn't feel like someone farted on your eyes and threw pocket fent at your eyes. 

as of 2/4/2026 the game actually runs without ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ itself, which is as much of an improvement as being able to make a phone call without crying, its the bare minimum. Before any of you turt stompers get on my ass, I have clocked my hours at the dino killing factory already. I bet most of you dont own neither an airfryer or a japanese edition mhgu on a japanese 3ds #smd. 

@capcum I need you to lock in and improve the screen brightness settings. Its not ideal that I have to google tricks to workaround the washed out light and color in the game, it looks like someone used sandpaper on my monitor on the most "balanced" setting. Im not even going to point out the lack of color at any other point that isnt happy weather ingame, its rancid. Also whats with adding super sayan anjanath but not the regular one, be for real man. Also add more hairstyles please, I need something other than generic white guy 1 - 4 and hipster clerk 6 - 9

p;s I need likes on this post so I can peer pressure evan into getting the game
